This life is so corrupt, I just want more stuff, instead of suffering, I wanna live life on both sides like a checker board, 


and really I’m bored, and sick of a basic life, I want a better life, I want a pleasant night, I want to feel like I’m right, for putting my all into this music, but even through all the music, 


I just want to be happy, as a kid I’d always wonder what it’s like to be happy, and as an adult I can imagine what it’s like to be happy, but I sip away hoping I achieve that feeling, 


and as I’m healing, I just want a sound that’s appealing, and I want money through the ceiling, 


I want joy through the ceiling, I want everything I ask for, not to sound too greedy, but I, still want it all, and if I fall, well at least I tried, 


I want a new stride, but this life’s a ride, and I’m waiting for my stop, I make so much music, that I wonder if I’ll ever stop, 


but I just wanna make it to the top, I wanna ball till I drop, I want strict authority like a cop, and I won’t stop, until I’ve claimed my spot, see this might not seem like a lot, 


but I’ve created a movement, and if I can move ment, they I’ll be sent, straight to success, this pain breaks my chest, but still I flow like I’m at my best, more wealth, 


my answer is yes, more vacations, my answer is yes, I often need rest, because of the things I take straight to the chest, I often feel like I’m hexed, what more can I confess, but if I’m being honest, all I want is more, context

Taking place 25 years after the events of Mortal Kombat™ (2011), the new generation of characters will discover that Outworld is not the only threat they face. text:
Dive into the heartfelt world of "LOST IN LOVE" by AMT NEXT, a song that captures the essence of longing, hope, and the search for true connection. With captivating lyrics and a hauntingly beautiful melody, "LOST IN LOVE" speaks to anyone who's ever felt alone on their journey through life, yet continues to hold out hope for a love that will bring them warmth and belonging.

"LOST IN LOVE" is a deeply emotional track, blending elements of pop and soul, wrapped in neon-lit imagery that reflects the urban loneliness so many feel. This song is perfect for late-night listening or those moments when you find yourself lost in thought, wondering if love is out there waiting. AMT NEXT takes you on a soulful journey with this single, highlighting vulnerability and resilience in the face of life's cold, empty roads.

 Listen to "LOST IN LOVE" and let the lyrics and melodies pull you into a world where the stars hold secrets, and a shining light offers hope on the darkest of nights. Experience the power of AMT NEXT's music as it brings to life the journey of searching, dreaming, and holding on to the belief that one day, love will come.

 Lyrics of "LOST IN LOVE":
I’m walking down empty road,
All alone, nowhere to go,
Looking for a heart to hold,
Somewhere out there in the cold.

I’m searching for someone to love me,
A place where I can just be free,
A beautiful world, a shining light,
To hold me close through the night.

I see the stars up in the sky,
But none of them can tell me why,
I’m waiting here, my heart’s so wide,
Hoping love will come and find.

I’m searching for someone to love me,
A place where I can just be free,
A beautiful world, a shining light,
To hold me close through the night.

Maybe one day, I’ll find the place,
Where I belong, in love’s embrace.

I’m searching for someone to love me,
A place where I can just be free,
A beautiful world, a shining light,
To hold me close through the night.

I’ll keep on walking, I’ll keep on dreaming,
Till love finds me, my heart is beating.

 Don't forget to Like, Comment, and Subscribe to support AMT NEXT and stay updated on future releases! Turn on notifications so you never miss a new song from AMT NEXT. Share this song if it resonated with you or if you know someone who’s also searching for that special connection.

text:
Gang violence is often portrayed in the media as an issue that is predominantly of young men shooting other young men. While this is tragic in its own right, Dr. Amy Faith Ho sheds a different light on this social issue. From her experience as a physician at a busy urban trauma center, Dr. Ho reframes gang violence as a man’s battle, but a woman’s war. 

Dr. Amy Faith Ho is an emergency medicine physician, writer and speaker. Her works include features in Forbes, TEDx, NPR, Chicago Tribune and media features on the TODAY Show, Discovery Channel and TLC. Dr. Ho takes a special interest in sharing a physician’s unique perspective on issues in society – violence, mental heath, addiction and healthcare policy – and uses her writing and speaking to do so.

This talk was given at a TEDx event using the TED conference format but independently organized by a local community. Learn more at http://ted.com/tedx
title: Why Guns and Violence will be the next Women’s Movement | Amy Ho | TEDxOakParkWomen

What Is CMT's Next Women Of Country Program? In this engaging video, we take a closer look at an exciting initiative in the world of country music that is dedicated to spotlighting emerging female talent. CMT's Next Women of Country Program, established in 2013, is making waves by providing support and opportunities for new female artists in the genre. Each year, a fresh class of artists is chosen to receive essential resources and exposure, helping them to connect with fans and industry professionals alike.

The program not only addresses the historical lack of representation for women in country music but also serves as a platform for these artists to showcase their unique voices. With features on CMT's television programming, streaming channels, and social media campaigns, the selected artists gain visibility that can significantly impact their careers. Mentorship from established artists further enhances their journey, providing guidance and support as they navigate the music landscape.

Join us as we explore how this initiative is shaping the future of country music, making it more inclusive and reflective of diverse experiences. Don't forget to subscribe for more updates on the latest trends and talents in the country music scene!

text:
ABOUT THIS GAME

Purchase Game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/27...

Experience legendary American trucks and deliver various cargoes across sunny California, sandy Nevada, and the Grand Canyon State of Arizona. American Truck Simulator takes you on a journey through the breathtaking landscapes and widely recognized landmarks around the States.

Game mechanics are based on the highly successful model from Euro Truck Simulator 2 and have been expanded with new features, creating the most captivating game experience from SCS Software.

American Truck Simulator puts you in the seat of a driver for hire entering the local freight market, making you work your way up to become an owner-operator, and go on to create one of the largest transportation companies in the United States.
Features
Drive highly detailed truck models officially licensed from iconic truck manufacturers.
Your truck is your new home. Make it yours by changing cabins, chassis, paintjobs, adding tuning accessories or more powerful engines.
Lots of different cargoes to choose: From food to machinery to hazard cargoes.
Multiple types of trailers – from reefers to flatbeds, from dumpers to lowboys and goosenecks.
The longest trailers (up to 53 ft) will challenge your skills and patience while hauling and during parking.
Deliver your cargoes to a rich variety of companies and locations like refineries, oil storage, gas stations, car factories, or roadworks.


Various simulation settings for trucking enthusiasts: Air brake simulation; different types of brakes: retarder, Jake brake, trailer brake; multiple types of transmissions straight from real trucks, brake intensity, and more.
Get the feel of being inside a real cabin: Adjust your seat, mirrors and position your head to get the best view of the road.
Drive safely, follow the rules and speed limits – police will fine you if you aren't careful!
Ensure that you are not delivering overweight cargo – you may be checked at the weigh scales.
Use the route adviser as your personal assistant during the travels.
Try the life of a truck driver for hire. By delivering the cargoes safely and improving your skills, become the owner of your own, successful company!

Build your own fleet of trucks, buy garages, hire drivers, manage your company for maximum profits.
Make your trucking time better by listening to your favorite songs via built-in music player or streaming your favorite radio stations.
Capture your favorite moments with a photo mode offering rich set of editing options.
Great support for steering wheels, gamepads and other input devices.
Long-time support of the game, including new features.
Obtain challenging Steam achievements and collect all hand-painted Steam trading cards.
World of Trucks
Take advantage of additional features of American Truck Simulator by joining our online community on World of Trucks, our center for virtual truckers all around the world interested in Euro Truck Simulator 2, American Truck Simulator and future SCS Software's truck simulators.

Use in-game Photo Mode to capture the best moments and share them with thousands of people who love trucks.
Favorite the images you like the most and return to them anytime in the future.
Discuss the screenshots with everyone using World of Trucks.
See the best images hand-picked by the game creators in Editor's Pick updated almost every day. Try to get your own screenshot on this list!
Upload and use your custom avatar and license plate in the game.
More features coming soon!

To join World of Trucks, simply sign up with your Steam account on the join page. You will need to own American Truck Simulator or Euro Truck Simulator 2 to join World of Trucks.

Next Fashion School è una Società con origini storiche risalenti al 1934, rappresenta il collegamento tra la solida tradizione di progettazione che caratterizza il Made in Italy e la creatività avanguardista che non ha confini di tempo e di spazio.

Nelle tre sedi di Bologna, Ancona e Padova si preparano studenti con una tecnica formativa vincente ed utilizzata in moltissime  aziende nazionali ed internazionali ma nel contempo i concept a cui ci si ispira sono sperimentali, proiettati al futuro e imperniati su studi di settore e di stile.

Next Fashion School supporta il talento dei giovani e dei professionisti dallo studio delle influenze alla realizzazione di un campionario, approfondendo le varie fasi con le metodologie più idonee.

text:
You never know where your next fashion adventure awaits…

The Sa Pa valley is without a doubt one of the most beautiful places I have visited. It’s a place that has undergone (and is still experiencing) dramatic change as tourism has exploded in the area.

While the Hmong and other groups native to the valley traditionally farmed to survive, farming on the terraced fields yields only enough to feed the families, without excess available for sale or export. 

With rising prices due to the valley’s ever-growing popularity, the locals have embraced tourism, teaching visitors about their traditions and lifestyle. 

Their skill at textile making and design is incredible! It was fascinating to get to experience it up close, and even more interesting to learn about the process behind the decorative elements (coming soon!). 

Have you ever visited Sa Pa? Or maybe it’s on your travel bucket list?

#vietnamtravel #vietnamfashion #sapavietnam #sapavalley #hmong #traditionalclothing

text:
I remember the day I mustered the courage to tell my dad that I didn't want to pursue a career in law practice. It was a tough conversation. Things became even more difficult when I admitted that I hadn't used the N20,000 Naira my uncle gave me to buy the "wig and gown" for law school graduation. I had instead, saved the money for my business startup.  What I wore on my call-to-bar day was borrowed and already returned.
Being a lawyer had bestowed upon my dad the title of "barrister father,".He couldn't comprehend why, after investing in my education, I wanted to abandon the noble legal profession and become an "ngwa road tailor."
My mom, however, had a different perspective on my decision. And who could blame her? She carried the weight of responsibility, knowing she played a role in what my dad considered a disgrace. As a tailor or seamstress herself, she involved me in her craft from a young age, having me operate her sewing machines. She would ask for my assistance at the workshop, and also encouraged me to sketch my ideas on her apprentice's cement papers, and guided me in sewing my designs.
Last week, I decided to pass on ''this disgrace'' of following your dream and passion to the younger generation. I chose to share my experience of pursuing dreams and passions with the younger generation. I opened my factory to let them explore my software, tools, and machinery. My goal is to expand their thinking, support and guide them in the journey of entrepreneurship, and introduce the fashion business as a potential career option. I think it's our responsibility to teach our children about entrepreneurship and create an environment that helps them envision the possibilities for their future.
I encourage every business owner or entrepreneur to embrace the incredible power we have as parents and role models to shape the destinies of our children. Just as my mother guided me toward my path, let's provide our kids with opportunities to explore and choose their dreams. Don't let the dollar-to-naira rate dishearten you, and never give up. Our children look up to us, relying on our resilience and determination. 
"No gree for anybody." Follow your dream

ME.zero: il successo della Sfilata Next 2019

I 48 esordienti di Next Fashion School by Carla Secoli il 6 giugno 2019 hanno mostrato ad ospiti e stampa la loro preparazione, creatività e tecnica sfilando con le proprie capsule collections in ME.zero.
In un mix coinvolgente di linee e volumi d’avanguardia e virtuosismi couture, nella cornice del Savoia Hotel Regency di Bologna abbiamo assistito alla sfilata di 80 outfits il cui concetto poliedrico dell’esaltazione dell’individuo è stato celebrato in tutte le sue forme e declinazioni.
Cinque i temi d’ispirazione:
• ME.over: i volumi esagerati, inaspettati, che esaltano l’individuo e le sue forme
• ME.freestyle: il casual comfy energizzato in chiave sportiva, colori vitaminici e preziosi dettagli intrecciati, supplied by Manifattura di Domodossola
• ME.fold: la sartorialità scandita da linee pulite e dettagli curati; pieghe e plissé in chiave contemporanea stravolgono l’uniformità esaltandone lo stile
• ME.bright: l’immaginario del Rinascimento come spunto di celebrazione dell’uomo, rielaborato con nuance che virano verso la luce
• ME.dark: la cupa atmosfera tra Rinascimento e Barocco Olandese rivive in un fusion style ombroso e scultoreo
La Next Generation osserva, progetta e crea con lo spirito di chi sa fare Moda.

Lấy cảm hứng từ hình ảnh "nhà ga" và "chuyến tàu", mà ở đó mỗi "toa tàu" tái hiện một phong cách thời trang riêng của từng thương hiệu và "nhà ga" là dấu mốc thể hiện sự đổi mới trong hành trình phát triển của HOANG PHUC International.

Sự kiện diễn ra ngay tại Saigon Centre với hàng loạt trải nghiệm thú vị đang chờ bạn:
 Chiêm ngưỡng không gian triển lãm vô cùng đặc sắc, trưng bày các sản phẩm độc đáo nhất từ các thương hiệu thời trang quốc tế: Kappa, Ecko Unltd., Superga, Staple, NINU&NICK. 
 Tham gia các hoạt động hấp dẫn: minigame, chụp hình check-in và nhận về những phần quà giá trị. 
  Đặc biệt, bạn sẽ được lắng nghe những chia sẻ và giao lưu chuyện thời trang cùng Kelbin - một trong những stylist hàng đầu tại Việt Nam.

text: FASHION GRADUATE ITALIA 2022- NEXT GENERATION LAB presenta #HEREANDNOW la Sfilata di NEXT FASHION SCHOOL a Fashion Graduate Italia 2022 .------------Il QUI e ORA come mantra di equilibrio, il bilanciamento tra gli opposti diventa nuovo concept d’ispirazione.Le analisi sociologiche sul consumatore mostrano che ognuno cerca il perfetto equilibrio per vivere phygital, giostrando la propria vita tra situazioni in contrasto ma che si integrano con fluidità.ON/ OFF accendere le interazioni digitali per condividere, per servizi e per esperienze, spegnere le connessioni per ritrovare calma, quiete, meditazione, rapporti umani.INDOOR/OUTDOOR vivere la casa, come culla performante e fare rete con la comunità esterna, attraverso interazioni sicure.Vivere gli spazi esterni per immergersi nello scenario naturale, apprezzandone la materialità.#hereandnow si compone della visione poliedrica delle capsule collections:1-color block life; 2-endless denim; 3-move in time; 4-look through; 5-silver era; 6-earth energy; 7-evanescent; 8-opposite vibe; 9-east flavour;--------9 capsule interpretano il concept, 44 outfit disegnati e realizzati da: Hana Abdollahi-Federica Alessi-Maria Chiara Basso-Vanessa Becker-Veronica Colpo-Chiara Dubini-Francesca Giovannini-Giulia Lucarelli-Sara Monticelli-Emmanuella Yaa – Serwah Ofori – Atta-Tomas Pirazzoli-Sofia Ricci-Giada Ripari-Sofia Santi-Irene Scrivano-Virginia Venturi. text:
Here is the winning designer, Rebekka Schuman and her models from San Clemente High School.

September 25, 2008 fashion event sponsored by TeenVogue and O'Neill Sportswear.

The program was born out of a vision by the company to have interns be involved with the creative design process where teams from 5 different High schools (Diamond Bar, Dana Hills, Sage Hill of Newport, San Clemente High school, and El Modena High school) where invited to shadow ONeill designers and ultimately make their own designs and garments. After this process, which took several months, they took these finished fashion designs to this Runway in front of their high school peers who in turn voted for the team they thought had the best design.

Moms, Dads, friends, and the students jammed into Seven Degrees to watch the five chosen contestants unveil their designs, each with a dress and a purse created with the help of a fashion mentor.

The five designers started out with sketches and worked on everything from design to runway production. They were also responsible for marketing their team, with several groups getting creative by making Myspace pages and holding school rallies.

STILLLEBEN | LAB presents a multimedia triptych featuring the following innovative fashion designers from Arnhem, The Netherlands: Pauline van Dongen, Elsien Gringhuis + Aliki van der Kruijs, Jef Montes.

The network Next Fashion develops and executes the innovation agenda for the Dutch fashion sector as part of CLICKNL and has a national and international reach. The network is centered around three parties representing the 'golden triangle':
ArtEZ Institute of the Arts (knowledge institutes), MODINT, Dutch Fashion, Textiles and Carpet Industry Association (industry) and the Province of Gelderland and the City of Arnhem (government).

The Innovation agenda of Next Fashion focuses around new and different values, definitions and dimensions for the Dutch fashion and textile industry. It deals with technological innovations that are changing the fashion making process such as smart fibers or 3D design systems. It also addresses societal challenges like the development of a circular economy as a more sustainable society is becoming a serious issue for the fashion consumer. 

Finally, Next Fashion aims to strengthen the industry's innovation system by connecting innovations from small scale designers with the industry's capacity for scaling.

text:
Knowing about the next fashion trend requires a combination of observation, research, and staying connected with the fashion industry. Here's a description of how you can keep up with the latest fashion trends:

Fashion Magazines and Blogs: Fashion magazines and blogs are a great source of inspiration and information. Subscribe to popular fashion magazines or follow influential fashion bloggers who regularly share updates on the latest trends, runway shows, and style forecasts. These platforms often feature interviews with designers, trend reports, and street style photography, offering valuable insights into upcoming fashion trends.

Runway Shows: Keep an eye on fashion weeks and runway shows held in major fashion capitals like Paris, Milan, London, and New York. Designers present their collections during these events, showcasing upcoming trends. By closely following these shows, you can identify emerging themes, color palettes, and silhouettes that may become popular in the coming seasons.

Social Media: Social media platforms like Instagram, Pinterest, and TikTok have become powerful tools for discovering fashion trends. Follow fashion influencers, designers, and brands on these platforms to get a sneak peek into their latest collections, collaborations, and styling ideas. Many fashion influencers share their daily outfits, providing real-time insights into what's currently in vogue.

Street Style: Street style photography offers a glimpse into how fashion enthusiasts interpret and incorporate trends into their daily outfits. Pay attention to street style blogs, Instagram accounts, or even by observing stylish individuals in your own city. Street style can often be an early indicator of emerging trends before they hit the mainstream.

Fashion Exhibitions and Trade Shows: Attend fashion exhibitions, trade shows, and pop-up events in your area. These events showcase the work of emerging designers, independent brands, and fashion innovators. Exploring these exhibitions can give you a firsthand look at unique designs and concepts that might influence future trends.

Trend Forecasting Services: Several companies and organizations specialize in trend forecasting. They analyze cultural, social, and economic factors to predict upcoming fashion trends. Subscribing to these services can provide you with comprehensive trend reports and valuable insights into the direction of the fashion industry.

Celebrities and Red Carpet Events: Pay attention to what celebrities and influencers are wearing to major red carpet events, award ceremonies, and fashion galas. Their choices often reflect the latest fashion trends and can provide inspiration for your own wardrobe.

Online Communities and Forums: Engage in online fashion communities and forums where fashion enthusiasts discuss trends, share ideas, and post about upcoming styles. These platforms allow you to interact with like-minded individuals and gain different perspectives on fashion trends.

Remember, fashion is subjective, and it's important to develop your personal style. While staying informed about the latest trends can be exciting, don't be afraid to experiment and make fashion choices that align with your individual preferences and personality.

Welcome to NEXT@Fashion InStyle, a groundbreaking initiative dedicated to reshaping the future of fashion and design. This innovative space, bringing together over 60 global material suppliers, is a vibrant hub for creativity and connectivity, presenting the latest materials in the garment industry. We are honoured to have Han Chong, founder and creative director of the internationally acclaimed brand Self-Portrait, as the ambassador.

In collaboration with five visionary local designers, NEXT@Fashion InStyle showcases the synergy of creative design, advanced material properties, smart technology, biodegradability, and upcycling techniques, highlighting the transformative potential of innovative materials in the fashion industry.

The initiative is organised by the Hong Kong Trade Development Council (HKTDC) and funded by the Cultural and Creative Industries Development Agency (CCIDA) of the Hong Kong SAR Government. Thailand is the Strategic Partner of NEXT@Fashion InStyle powered by Thailand Creative Culture Agency (THACCA) and the National Soft Power Development Committee.

*Explore the Beauty of Ethiopian Traditional Dress *

Welcome to our channel, where the timeless elegance of Ethiopian traditional dress comes to life! Whether you're a fashion enthusiast, a cultural explorer, or someone who loves to celebrate heritage, our videos have something for everyone.

Discover the rich diversity of Ethiopian attire, from the iconic *Habesha Kemis* to vibrant *tibeb* patterns, and learn about the stories and traditions behind these stunning outfits. We showcase traditional clothing for all age groups—men, women, and children—ensuring there's something for everyone to enjoy.

✨ *What You'll Find Here:*

Join us on a journey through Ethiopia's cultural tapestry, where every outfit tells a story. Don’t forget to like, share, and comment on your favorite looks, and hit that subscribe button for more exciting content every week!

Stay connected with us for the latest trends in Ethiopian fashion, and let’s celebrate culture together!  The habesha kemis has been a cultural staple of Ethiopian style for centuries. Today's designers are reimagining this timeless garment in fresh, fashion-forward ways. By subtly modernizing elements of the traditional kemis, Ethiopian designers ensure it remains relevant while preserving cultural heritage. 

With countless styles, the versatile kemis can transform your look for any occasion. Switch from an embroidered kemis for a dinner party to a relaxed cotton version for lounging at home. Comfortable and culturally celebratory, the habesha kemis is a wardrobe essential. 

The new 2023 habesha kemis collection beautifully blends tradition and innovation. Handcrafted with exquisite detail, each kemis incorporates traditional Ethiopian patterns into contemporary silhouettes. Rediscover your cultural pride and unique style with these modern takes on a time-honored classic.

text:
The AFI Fastrack Prize, otherwise known as the “Young Designer of the Year” Award is awarded by Africa Fashion International to exceptional and talented emerging fashion designers in South Africa. The Fastrack Prize is a culmination of a series of intense training and mentorship in the fashion business including a competition element where finalist compete for a prize. 

As South Africa celebrates “30 Years of Freedom” – a monumental moment in South African history – Africa Fashion International graduates the AFI Fastrack Program Class of 2023 under the theme “30 Years of Fashion Expression”.   
 
Following the journey of the AFI Fastrack Finalists in the final week of the competition, this documentary from Africa Fashion International gives you an insider view of the fashion incubator program that has been transformative to South African fashion since its inception in 2011.  
 
Each year, thousands of local talents apply, and the business is tasked with selecting seven finalists, who go through the AFI Fastrack Programme. The finalists are given opportunities to produce for Cape Town Fashion Week and Joburg Fashion Week runways and plug into AFI’s calendar of events, attend enriching training sessions and seminars. The winners not only receive a cash prize but are also afforded an opportunity to join AFI PRIVE and given all the support and resources as leading contemporary designers for the brand. 
 
Through this year-long incubator programme, seven young designers are challenged to build on the talent and passion behind their brands by developing their business acumen. The programme puts an emphasis on concrete business skills, economic sustainability, quality and craftsmanship, market-awareness, and innovative entrepreneurship – all the makings of a successful fashion business.  
 
The AFI Fastrack Prize is awarded in 3 categories: The “Young Designer of the Year” receives a transformative cash prize and internship. Two finalists are awarded for Craftsmanship, Creativity & Innovation.  
 
The AFI Fastrack Prize is about identifying and nurturing the next generation of global fashion leaders. It exemplifies AFI’s belief in excellence and desire to uncover the genius/brilliance that lives on the African continent. These are the values AFI instil in these emergent designers, as they are shaped into the future stars of African fashion.

text:
Ogni individuo racchiude una grande forza: un potere infinito e autorigenerante di flessibilità che si manifesta con sfaccettature e sequenze prismatiche diverse tra loro ma mirabilmente coese ed armoniche.
Siamo il frutto di ciò che abbiamo visto, che abbiamo provato ma anche dei nostri sogni ed aspirazioni che trasformano il frutto stesso nel divenire del tempo.
È questo il potere dell’individuo, che giocando ed interagendo con la collettività, genera meraviglie. È l’unicità di un mix mai replicabile ma soprattutto di cui essere fieri e di cui prendersi cura.
L’abbigliamento sta virando in modo ormai irreversibile verso lo stile individuale, a tratti definito, a tratti contraddittorio, sempre più lontano dal mainstream che ci vorrebbe omologati.
La Next Generation interpreta questa energia infinita con la positività e la creatività delle menti talentuose, mostrando fotogrammi di presente che si specchiano nei desideri del futuro.

text:
A statement for the driver: The BMW Vision M NEXT gives a preview of what the electrified future of the BMW M brand might look like. The BMW Vision M NEXT is a progressive sports car that makes a clear and self-confident statement both in terms of its appearance and its interaction.

For more information, visit: https://redirect.bmw.com/bmw-vision-m...
To experience the BMW Vision M NEXT in four additional ways, click here: http://b.mw/com-mnext

With its sporty proportions and just a few precise lines, the BMW Vision M NEXT portrays a strong character. At the front, orange Air Blades extend from both sides towards the centre of the vehicle and, in conjunction with the blade-shaped air intake below the kidney grille, create a clear racing aesthetic. From a side view, the low-slung, wedge-shaped sports car silhouette, the contours ascending towards the rear and the diagonal, orange colour separation give the impression that the BMW Vision M NEXT is surging forward even when standing still. The rear sculpture combines the sides optically, thus emphasising the vehicle’s width.

The idea of reduced simplicity brings together exterior and interior.
The BOOST Pod is the key element in the interior. Intelligent technologies support the driver and deliver the right contents at the right time. Immersed and focused, the driver becomes the ultimate driver.

The Power-PHEV drive of the BMW Vision M NEXT allows to choose between four electrically driven wheels or a purist rear-wheel drive – purely electrically or accelerated by turbocharged 4-cylinder petrol engine.  

The design of the BMW Vision M NEXT is the result of an internal contest. BMW designers competed against one another with their hand-drawn sketches and visualisations. Several rounds took place to select the best designs until, finally, the draft to be implemented was picked out. The process from initial idea to complete vision vehicle took roughly 18 months.

Sound by Hans Zimmer.

text:
Episode: White Cyc Lighting

Introduction:

Welcome everyone to an in-studio episode where I teach you some of my favorite lighting set ups for shooting on a white Cyc, or cyclorama! 

What is a cyc? A cyc is used to hide the corner where the wall meets the floor. It gives the illusion of an infinite background space. You can also achieve this look with rolls of colored or white seamless paper. Cycs are almost always painted white which makes lighting much easier, BUT it can also make your lighting look flat. Knowing how to shoot on a white cyc is imperative to your success as a photographer. White cycs are used for fashion, products, jewelry and also video so eventually you will probably end up shooting on one. We're going to be using Profoto lights but you can use any lights and achieve the same looks.

0:01 Intro
2:03 1st Lighting Setup- "Soft Front Light Double Black Cards"
